Name: 69 Summon Succubus
About the game: 69 Summon Sucubus - is a game in which you take on the role of a succubus trainer. You have become the owner of a magic book that allows you to summon the succubus Lilith. You need to choose skills for training and complete tasks. After each workout, your succubus will get stronger. Lilith can become very powerful, but for this she will need to be trained diligently. Features Atmospheric music Meditative gameplay Mini games for pumping Heart-to-heart conversation with a succubus
